other workshops here at Frontend Masters.

43
00:03:10.845 --> 00:03:13.705
We've seen how permission and
security works.

44
00:03:13.705 --> 00:03:18.721
Compatibility, that for a lot of
APIs that we have mentioned today,

45
00:03:18.721 --> 00:03:22.710
it works on Safari, on Android,
on iOS, and Chrome.

46
00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:25.344
For others, it depends.

47
00:03:25.344 --> 00:03:30.938
Then we get into API for sensors,
location, and input, such as multi-touch.

48
00:03:30.938 --> 00:03:34.848
Then speech, voice, and
camera, hardware and devices.

49
00:03:34.848 --> 00:03:38.407
And finally integration with
the operating system, and

50
00:03:38.407 --> 00:03:41.235
some of them are actually
PWA capabilities.

51
